# Stow local ignore file
# Files and patterns listed here will NOT be symlinked when running `stow pnpm`
#
# Nothing in this directory belongs in $HOME. The pnpm/ folder is reference
# material: docs and a template that gets copied into project repos manually.
# Global pnpm config is applied via `pnpm config set ... --global`, not stow.

README\.md
pnpm-workspace\.yaml\.template
global-rc\.example
